    {
      "id": "optimistic_5_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in style with this fantastic find! This car is in good condition and has been well-maintained, offering a smooth and reliable driving experience you can count on. It shows a few minor signs of careful use, but overall it\u2019s a solid, attractive vehicle that\u2019s ready for many more miles of adventure. If you're looking for a dependable ride that still looks great, this is the one for you!",
      "price": 34500.0,
